{"id":"2a0ead3f-2dec-48ca-ad5e-9f63eb2daed6","name":"The oracles","description":"<p>|| ｆａｎｔａｓｙ</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 211, 187)\">A mysterious visitor had arrived, bringing an unexpected change to the three oracles Tiserias, Caspian and Orin. While Caspian is eager to finally leave the desolate island where the temple was located on, Tiserias wants to remain in that gilded cage they had been calling their home for years now. What does the mysterious visitor want? And who are they?</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 87, 69)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #a3d3bb; color: inherit\">Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ</mark></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_59d6c91b-e36b-4499-b6d2-b54ceddfb370.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 87, 69)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #a3d3bb; color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴇᴍᴘʟᴇ ᴏғ ɢᴇᴘʜʏʀᴀs ɪs ᴏғᴛᴇɴ sᴇᴇɴ ᴀs ᴀ ʙʀɪᴅɢᴇ ʙᴇᴛᴡᴇᴇɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴏʀᴛᴀʟs ᴀɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ɢᴏᴅs.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_094a96e1-42ae-452a-ae16-e85033effb66.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 87, 69)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #a3d3bb; color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴏᴏᴍ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴀɢɪᴄ ʜᴀᴘᴘᴇɴs- ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀɴᴄɪɴɢ ʀɪᴛᴜᴀʟ ᴛᴀᴋᴇs ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ɪɴ ᴀ ʀᴏᴜɴᴅ ʀᴏᴏᴍ, ᴀʟsᴏ ᴄᴀʟʟᴇᴅ ᴛʜᴇ sʏɴᴅᴇsɪs ʀᴏᴏᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ɪs ᴛʜᴇ ᴏɴʟʏ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʀᴀᴄʟᴇs ᴍᴀʏ sʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇᴍsᴇʟᴠᴇs.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 87, 69)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #a3d3bb; color: inherit\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_523275bb-ee71-482f-9fe2-e16ed72e9049.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʀᴀᴄʟᴇs ᴍᴀʏ ᴏɴʟʏ ʀᴇᴠᴇᴀʟ ᴛʜᴇᴍsᴇʟᴠᴇs ᴡʜᴇɴ ᴛʜᴇʏ ᴅᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴏᴜᴛsɪᴅᴇʀs, ᴏᴛʜᴇʀᴡɪsᴇ ᴏɴʟʏ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ sʜɪʟᴏᴜᴇᴛᴛᴇs ʙᴇʜɪɴᴅ